      <title>瑞士称已冻结价值 142 亿美元的俄罗斯资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/switzerland-says-it-s-blocked-14-2-billion-of-russian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士冻结了在该国持有的130亿瑞士法郎（142亿美元）的俄罗斯资产，其中包括俄罗斯央行超过70亿瑞士法郎的储备和资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/switzerland-says-it-s-blocked-14-2-billion-of-russian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 07:10:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高级外交官称中国普京将与欧盟的风险关系联系起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-putin-ties-risk-relations-with-eu-top-diplomat-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟驻亚洲最高外交官表示，如果中国致力于改善关系，就需要对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰采取立场，并控制其与欧盟的巨额贸易顺差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/china-s-putin-ties-risk-relations-with-eu-top-diplomat-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:43:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国预算赤字超支，打击亨特减税希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-budget-deficit-overshoots-in-setback-for-hunt-s-tax-cut-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府上一财年的借款超出了官方预测，凸显了财政大臣杰里米·亨特在考虑大选前减税时面临的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-budget-deficit-overshoots-in-setback-for-hunt-s-tax-cut-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国商会称美国企业对投资中国仍持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/us-firms-still-cautious-about-investing-in-china-amcham-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个商业团体表示，由于政策的不可预测性，美国公司对在中国投资持谨慎态度，因为北京方面正在努力吸引外国资金来提振经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/us-firms-still-cautious-about-investing-in-china-amcham-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 06:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>祖马的政党希望将南非的土地和矿山国有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/zuma-s-party-wants-to-nationalize-land-mines-in-south-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非前总统雅各布·祖马(Jacob Zuma)新成立的政党在5月29日选举前发布的竞选宣言中誓言将土地和银行国有化、退出国际刑事法院并扩大社会保障网络。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/zuma-s-party-wants-to-nationalize-land-mines-in-south-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大选临近，日本前首相麻生太郎将与特朗普会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/japan-s-former-premier-aso-to-meet-trump-as-us-election-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本前首相麻生太郎将于周二晚上在美国会见前总统唐纳德·特朗普。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/japan-s-former-premier-aso-to-meet-trump-as-us-election-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 05:22:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两架马来西亚海军直升机坠毁，造成10人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/two-malaysia-navy-helicopters-crash-killing-10-personnel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，马来西亚海军阅兵排练期间，两架直升机坠毁，机上 10 名军事人员全部遇难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/two-malaysia-navy-helicopters-crash-killing-10-personnel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:52:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国敦促美国向基辅派遣另一个爱国者导弹系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-raises-pressure-on-us-to-step-up-kyiv-air-defense-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨政府正在敦促美国向乌克兰提供至少一套爱国者反导系统，以帮助缩小俄罗斯在升级一系列攻击之际的防空差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-raises-pressure-on-us-to-step-up-kyiv-air-defense-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 04:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在悉尼袭击帖子澳大利亚法庭听证会上失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/musk-loses-australia-court-hearing-on-sydney-knife-attack-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的社交网络 X 遭到澳大利亚法院的临时禁令，要求其删除刺伤袭击的视频，这引发了该社交网络所有者的愤怒回应，指责政府进行审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/musk-loses-australia-court-hearing-on-sydney-knife-attack-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 00:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在卢旺达驱逐计划惨败后面临法庭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/sunak-s-rwanda-deportation-bill-to-become-law-after-long-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理里希·苏纳克在一场暴露了保守党内部深刻分歧的斗争中确保通过具有里程碑意义的移民立法后，发誓要克服进一步的挑战，并继续推进飞往卢旺达的驱逐航班。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/sunak-s-rwanda-deportation-bill-to-become-law-after-long-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 23:21:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
